ðŸ”¹ General Logic

Outer loop â†’ number of rows

Inner loop â†’ number of columns

Print statement â†’ pattern shape

5
â­ Example: Right Triangle Star Pattern
*
* *
* * *
* * * *

int n = 4;
for(int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
    for(int j = 1; j <= i; j++) {
        cout << "* ";
    }
    cout << endl;
}

